{"id": 1800, "genre": 1001, "title": "在公共议题讨论上，你烦哪种人？", "description": "你都拎不清什么事，你就劝我大度。（题图来自：林小妖）", "record_count": 4928, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20170713103124I67mEVLCgiXpPnzZ.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2017-07-13T03:00:16Z", "options": [{"id": 221440, "content": "无关刷屏", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 978594}, {"id": 221696, "content": "“反正这跟我没关系”", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 898495}, {"id": 222209, "content": "无语于", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 855755}, {"id": 221442, "content": "关你什么事", "image": null, "praise_count": 17, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 879179}, {"id": 221698, "content": "自己没观点，等别人来洗脑。", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 475133}, {"id": 222722, "content": "没素质，不假思索的骂人", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1081964}, {"id": 221443, "content": "啥都不懂还瞎BB的人", "image": null, "praise_count": 133, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 886824}, {"id": 228099, "content": "一言不合就人身攻击，看到不合心意的便开始情绪化", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1099657}, {"id": 221700, "content": "管闲事，不喜欢\n\n\n滚！", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1071466}, {"id": 222468, "content": "无脑吹和无脑黑“人家美国到底是民主国家啊……”“中国没有愚民政策！！！”", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1081142}, {"id": 221445, "content": "骂人的人。", "image": null, "praise_count": 70, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1076104}, {"id": 221701, "content": "'社会'人", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1078063}, {"id": 224773, "content": "不理解别人，不尊重自己", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1082744}, {"id": 221446, "content": "哎呀，这个有点危险啊", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1077307}, {"id": 221703, "content": "“你都拎不清什么事，就劝我大度。”", "image": null, "praise_count": 15, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 256134}, {"id": 222215, "content": "故意站在大多数人的对立面，用自以为的“上帝视角”显得自己特立独行，反驳别人的一切，其实自己才最愚蠢", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1079933}, {"id": 235527, "content": "上来也讲不出自己的观点，就只会说：反正你也不懂和你多说你也不知道。显得自己高人一等的人。其实大家都是在讨论，如果觉得自己很懂可以心平气和说说各自观点啊。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 142839}, {"id": 221448, "content": "还有n秒种，键盘侠到场……", "image": null, "praise_count": 15, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 293992}, {"id": 221449, "content": "大嘴巴", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1077461}, {"id": 224777, "content": "奴性思维的人", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1088136}, {"id": 221450, "content": "说话带情绪的人", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1077459}, {"id": 221706, "content": "装作自己啥都懂，啥都看得开。", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 181495}, {"id": 221962, "content": "嘴上ok，但其他所有的表现都体现出反抗的意思", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1078727}, {"id": 221451, "content": "看看日本美国做的东西质量就是好，中国不行……，看看玫瑰日本德国科技多发达，中国不行……，看看美国日本空气多好，中国不行……???", "image": null, "praise_count": 81, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 594999}, {"id": 221707, "content": "中年感。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 181495}, {"id": 221452, "content": "无脑圣母", "image": null, "praise_count": 37, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1054564}, {"id": 221454, "content": "不喜欢刻意引起仇恨的言论导向", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1023437}, {"id": 221710, "content": "膜，最烦这个，真的无聊", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1078017}, {"id": 222734, "content": "不会考虑别人", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 712994}, {"id": 221455, "content": "没事儿，你们决定吧？我都可以。。。等决定好，又这个不行那个不行。", "image": null, "praise_count": 20, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1077475}, {"id": 221456, "content": "瞎逼逼的", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1077160}, {"id": 221457, "content": "键盘手\n", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 839642}, {"id": 221458, "content": "讨厌那种同意自己的言论是理所当然，不同意的就是需要被咒死的异端?", "image": null, "praise_count": 12, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 772313}, {"id": 221459, "content": "愚民", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1077481}, {"id": 221715, "content": "事实是，小粉红确实是水军……", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 870248}, {"id": 222483, "content": "武断。拿外国和中国使劲作对比 别人都是好的 我们都不完整。服了。还有那种口碑还不错的电影 理性讨论就好了 偏要说“全民吹捧 而我却..” 然后就语气特别冲的一个劲说不好 ", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1080872}, {"id": 221460, "content": "思想奇葩", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 881681}, {"id": 221461, "content": "就烦题目说的这种，什么都劝你大度，我爹就是这种人的强势版，唉！", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1077482}, {"id": 221462, "content": "你们这样没用的。", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 118131}, {"id": 221718, "content": "经常开玩笑，特别过分还不自知的人", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1077939}, {"id": 224790, "content": "乱跟风，还老说别人不行，老说你行你上啊", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1025941}, {"id": 221463, "content": "贴标签。小粉红，美分狗。批评国家就滚出去。惹不起惹不起。", "image": null, "praise_count": 124, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 535937}, {"id": 221719, "content": "用和事件本身无关的道德标准职责当事人", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 927076}, {"id": 221464, "content": "无脑黑一方，无脑捧另一方，例如中国和美国", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 198685}, 